longBusinessSummary: Gulf West Security Network, Inc., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the engineering, design, installation, remote monitoring, and after-market servicing of residential and commercial electronic security, and home automation systems in the United States. It offers home burglar, fire, and medical alarm systems, as well as fully integrated business security and automation systems. The company is based in Lafayette, Louisiana.
